51
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:42,680
- Duduk.
- Saya mahu duduk bertentangan dengan Dia.

52
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,760
Pergi ke hadapan, duduk.

53
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,600
Terima kasih.

54
