Awak, Encik He, dan Fei semua minum.

82
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,640
Tetapi tidak dengan saya. Jangan pedulikan saya, ya?

83
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,160
lepas tu jom.

84
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,800
minum.

85
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,840
Saya memerhati awak.

86
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,400
Mari, gali.

87
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,160
Filem ini agak bagus.

88
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,080
Sudah tentu ia bagus.

89
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,720
Pengantin perempuan nampak cantik bertudung.

90
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,200
Ya!

91
