Dia sangat adil dan bersih, seperti bidadari.

92
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,960
Awak pun tak teruk.

93
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,800
Saya sangat suka Marlon Brando.

94
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,400
